{
  "video_id": "tjkrKA1cVdU",
  "title": "3 ways to plan for the (very) long term | Ari Wallach",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12620.0,
      "end_time": 15995.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ve been \"futuring,\" which is a term I made up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16200.0,
      "end_time": 17276.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17300.0,
      "end_time": 18516.0,
      "text": "about three seconds ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18540.0,
      "end_time": 21355.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been futuring for about 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21380.0,
      "end_time": 24715.0,
      "text": "and when I first started, I would sit down with people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24740.0,
      "end_time": 27636.0,
      "text": "and say, \"Hey, let&#39;s talk 10, 20 years out.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27660.0,
      "end_time": 29436.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;d say, \"Great.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29460.0,
      "end_time": 31956.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve been seeing that time horizon"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31980.0,
      "end_time": 34360.0,
      "text": "get shorter and shorter"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 35676.0,
      "text": "and shorter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35700.0,
      "end_time": 39760.0,
      "text": "so much so that I met with a CEO two months ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39100.0,
      "end_time": 41476.0,
      "text": "and I said -- we started our initial conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41500.0,
      "end_time": 45236.0,
      "text": "He goes, \"I love what you do. I want to talk about the next six months.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 46860.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47860.0,
      "end_time": 50996.0,
      "text": "We have a lot of problems that we are facing."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51200.0,
      "end_time": 53740.0,
      "text": "These are civilizational-scale problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55340.0,
      "end_time": 56780.0,
      "text": "The issue though is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57420.0,
      "end_time": 59116.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t solve them"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59140.0,
      "end_time": 61716.0,
      "text": "using the mental models that we use right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61740.0,
      "end_time": 63316.0,
      "text": "to try and solve these problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63340.0,
      "end_time": 65996.0,
      "text": "Yes, a lot of great technical work is being done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66200.0,
      "end_time": 71396.0,
      "text": "but there is a problem that we need to solve for a priori, before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71420.0,
      "end_time": 74220.0,
      "text": "if we want to really move the needle on those big problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74980.0,
      "end_time": 76716.0,
      "text": "\"Short-termism.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76740.0,
      "end_time": 79196.0,
      "text": "Right? There&#39;s no marches. There&#39;s no bracelets."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79220.0,
      "end_time": 83760.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no petitions that you can sign to be against short-termism."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83100.0,
      "end_time": 85916.0,
      "text": "I tried to put one up, and no one signed."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85940.0,
      "end_time": 87155.0,
      "text": "It was weird."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87180.0,
      "end_time": 88380.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89100.0,
      "end_time": 92116.0,
      "text": "But it prevents us from doing so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92140.0,
      "end_time": 94836.0,
      "text": "Short-termism, for many reasons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94860.0,
      "end_time": 97756.0,
      "text": "has pervaded every nook and cranny of our reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 97780.0,
      "end_time": 99356.0,
      "text": "I just want you to take a second"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 99380.0,
      "end_time": 103196.0,
      "text": "and just think about an issue that you&#39;re thinking, working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 103220.0,
      "end_time": 105196.0,
      "text": "It could be personal, it could be at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105220.0,
      "end_time": 107276.0,
      "text": "or it could be move-the-needle world stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107300.0,
      "end_time": 109636.0,
      "text": "and think about how far out you tend to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 109660.0,
      "end_time": 112179.0,
      "text": "about the solution set for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 113740.0,
      "end_time": 118155.0,
      "text": "Because short-termism prevents the CEO"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118180.0,
      "end_time": 120820.0,
      "text": "from buying really expensive safety equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121740.0,
      "end_time": 123716.0,
      "text": "It&#39;ll hurt the bottom line."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123740.0,
      "end_time": 125539.0,
      "text": "So we get the Deepwater Horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126220.0,
      "end_time": 128955.0,
      "text": "Short-termism prevents teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128979.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132516.0,
      "text": "from spending quality one-on-one time with their students."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132540.0,
      "end_time": 134676.0,
      "text": "So right now in America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134700.0,
      "end_time": 137540.0,
      "text": "a high school student drops out every 26 seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139180.0,
      "end_time": 141916.0,
      "text": "Short-termism prevents Congress --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141940.0,
      "end_time": 144556.0,
      "text": "sorry if there&#39;s anyone in here from Congress --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144580.0,
      "end_time": 146116.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146140.0,
      "end_time": 148196.0,
      "text": "or not really that sorry --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 148220.0,
      "end_time": 150436.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150460.0,
      "end_time": 153636.0,
      "text": "from putting money into a real infrastructure bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 153660.0,
      "end_time": 156276.0,
      "text": "So what we get is the I-35W bridge collapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 156300.0,
      "end_time": 158116.0,
      "text": "over the Mississippi a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 158140.0,
      "end_time": 159339.0,
      "text": "13 killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160580.0,
      "end_time": 163340.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t always like this. We did the Panama Canal."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164420.0,
      "end_time": 166676.0,
      "text": "We pretty much have eradicated global polio."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 166700.0,
      "end_time": 169500.0,
      "text": "We did the transcontinental railroad, the Marshall Plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170380.0,
      "end_time": 174180.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just big, physical infrastructure problems and issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174740.0,
      "end_time": 176636.0,
      "text": "Women&#39;s suffrage, the right to vote."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176660.0,
      "end_time": 179436.0,
      "text": "But in our short-termist time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 179460.0,
      "end_time": 181956.0,
      "text": "where everything seems to happen right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181980.0,
      "end_time": 186476.0,
      "text": "and we can only think out past the next tweet or timeline post,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186500.0,
      "end_time": 188516.0,
      "text": "we get hyper-reactionary."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 188540.0,
      "end_time": 189820.0,
      "text": "So what do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190700.0,
      "end_time": 193956.0,
      "text": "We take people who are fleeing their war-torn country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193980.0,
      "end_time": 195236.0,
      "text": "and we go after them."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195260.0,
      "end_time": 198876.0,
      "text": "We take low-level drug offenders, and we put them away for life."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198900.0,
      "end_time": 201276.0,
      "text": "And then we build McMansions without even thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201300.0,
      "end_time": 204166.0,
      "text": "about how people are going to get between them and their job."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 204190.0,
      "end_time": 205670.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a quick buck."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 206580.0,
      "end_time": 208916.0,
      "text": "Now, the reality is, for a lot of these problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208940.0,
      "end_time": 211716.0,
      "text": "there are some technical fixes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 211740.0,
      "end_time": 212956.0,
      "text": "a lot of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 212980.0,
      "end_time": 216516.0,
      "text": "I call these technical fixes sandbag strategies."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 216540.0,
      "end_time": 218236.0,
      "text": "So you know there&#39;s a storm coming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220995.0,
      "text": "the levee is broken, no one&#39;s put any money into it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221200.0,
      "end_time": 222836.0,
      "text": "you surround your home with sandbags."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 222860.0,
      "end_time": 224660.0,
      "text": "And guess what? It works."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226420.0,
      "end_time": 228435.0,
      "text": "Storm goes away, the water level goes down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228460.0,
      "end_time": 229836.0,
      "text": "you get rid of the sandbags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229860.0,
      "end_time": 232380.0,
      "text": "and you do this storm after storm after storm."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233740.0,
      "end_time": 235220.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the insidious thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235940.0,
      "end_time": 237835.0,
      "text": "A sandbag strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237860.0,
      "end_time": 239600.0,
      "text": "can get you reelected."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240140.0,
      "end_time": 241516.0,
      "text": "A sandbag strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241540.0,
      "end_time": 243500.0,
      "text": "can help you make your quarterly numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246600.0,
      "end_time": 249360.0,
      "text": "Now, if we want to move forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249600.0,
      "end_time": 251836.0,
      "text": "into a different future than the one we have right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 251860.0,
      "end_time": 253916.0,
      "text": "because I don&#39;t think we&#39;ve hit --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 253940.0,
      "end_time": 255916.0,
      "text": "2016 is not peak civilization."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 255940.0,
      "end_time": 257276.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257300.0,
      "end_time": 259760.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s some more we can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259100.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263716.0,
      "text": "But my argument is that unless we shift our mental models and our mental maps"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 263740.0,
      "end_time": 266760.0,
      "text": "on how we think about the short,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266100.0,
      "end_time": 267796.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not going to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 267820.0,
      "end_time": 270796.0,
      "text": "So what I&#39;ve developed is something called \"longpath,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 270820.0,
      "end_time": 272556.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 272580.0,
      "end_time": 276515.0,
      "text": "And longpath isn&#39;t a kind of one-and-done exercise."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 276540.0,
      "end_time": 279236.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sure everyone here at some point has done an off-site"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281356.0,
      "text": "with a lot of Post-It notes and whiteboards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 281380.0,
      "end_time": 284276.0,
      "text": "and you do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 284300.0,
      "end_time": 286756.0,
      "text": "no offense to the consultants in here who do that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 286780.0,
      "end_time": 288395.0,
      "text": "and you do a long-term plan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 288420.0,
      "end_time": 290860.0,
      "text": "and then two weeks later, everyone forgets about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 292460.0,
      "end_time": 295659.0,
      "text": "Right? Or a week later. If you&#39;re lucky, three months."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 296660.0,
      "end_time": 300236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a practice because it&#39;s not necessarily a thing that you do."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 304360.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a process where you have to revisit different ways of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 304600.0,
      "end_time": 306476.0,
      "text": "for every major decision that you&#39;re working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 306500.0,
      "end_time": 308980.0,
      "text": "So I want to go through those three ways of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 309780.0,
      "end_time": 312340.0,
      "text": "So the first: transgenerational thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 313180.0,
      "end_time": 315396.0,
      "text": "I love the philosophers:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 315420.0,
      "end_time": 317236.0,
      "text": "Plato, Socrates, Habermas, Heidegger."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 318460.0,
      "text": "I was raised on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 319860.0,
      "end_time": 321796.0,
      "text": "But they all did one thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 321820.0,
      "end_time": 323796.0,
      "text": "that didn&#39;t actually seem like a big deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 323820.0,
      "end_time": 326156.0,
      "text": "until I really started kind of looking into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 326180.0,
      "end_time": 327996.0,
      "text": "And they all took,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 328200.0,
      "end_time": 330916.0,
      "text": "as a unit of measure for their entire reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 330940.0,
      "end_time": 332893.0,
      "text": "of what it meant to be virtuous and good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 333700.0,
      "end_time": 334900.0,
      "text": "the single lifespan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 335780.0,
      "end_time": 336979.0,
      "text": "from birth to death."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 337460.0,
      "end_time": 339515.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s a problem with these issues:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 339540.0,
      "end_time": 340956.0,
      "text": "they stack up on top of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 340980.0,
      "end_time": 344116.0,
      "text": "because the only way we know how to do something good in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 344140.0,
      "end_time": 346356.0,
      "text": "is if we do it between our birth and our death."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 346380.0,
      "end_time": 348760.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we&#39;re programmed to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 348100.0,
      "end_time": 350556.0,
      "text": "If you go to the self-help section in any bookstore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 350580.0,
      "end_time": 351820.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s all about you."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 353220.0,
      "end_time": 355760.0,
      "text": "Which is great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355100.0,
      "end_time": 358200.0,
      "text": "unless you&#39;re dealing with some of these major issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 359780.0,
      "end_time": 362219.0,
      "text": "And so with transgenerational thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 363100.0,
      "end_time": 365756.0,
      "text": "which is really kind of transgenerational ethics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 365780.0,
      "end_time": 369395.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re able to expand how you think about these problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 369420.0,
      "end_time": 372180.0,
      "text": "what is your role in helping to solve them."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 373540.0,
      "end_time": 377700.0,
      "text": "Now, this isn&#39;t something that just has to be done at the Security Council chamber."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 378300.0,
      "end_time": 381556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that you can do in a very kind of personal way."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 381580.0,
      "end_time": 385996.0,
      "text": "So every once in a while, if I&#39;m lucky, my wife and I like to go out to dinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 386200.0,
      "end_time": 389275.0,
      "text": "and we have three children under the age of seven."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 389300.0,
      "end_time": 391729.0,
      "text": "So you can imagine it&#39;s a very peaceful, quiet meal."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 391753.0,
      "end_time": 392955.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 392980.0,
      "end_time": 398556.0,
      "text": "So we sit down and literally all I want to do is just eat and chill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 398580.0,
      "end_time": 401236.0,
      "text": "and my kids have a completely and totally different idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 402836.0,
      "text": "of what we&#39;re going to be doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 402860.0,
      "end_time": 405196.0,
      "text": "And so my first idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 405220.0,
      "end_time": 407116.0,
      "text": "is my sandbag strategy, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 407140.0,
      "end_time": 409476.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s to go into my pocket and take out the iPhone"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 409500.0,
      "end_time": 410956.0,
      "text": "and give them \"Frozen\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 410980.0,
      "end_time": 413940.0,
      "text": "or some other bestselling game thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 415600.0,
      "end_time": 418756.0,
      "text": "And then I stop"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 418780.0,
      "end_time": 423356.0,
      "text": "and I have to kind of put on this transgenerational thinking cap."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 423380.0,
      "end_time": 426356.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t do this in the restaurant, because it would be bizarre,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 426380.0,
      "end_time": 427676.0,
      "text": "but I have to --"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 427700.0,
      "end_time": 430316.0,
      "text": "I did it once, and that&#39;s how I learned it was bizarre."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 430340.0,
      "end_time": 431356.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 431380.0,
      "end_time": 435500.0,
      "text": "And you have to kind of think, \"OK, I can do this.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 437980.0,
      "text": "But what is this teaching them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 439300.0,
      "end_time": 441916.0,
      "text": "So what does it mean if I actually bring some paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 441940.0,
      "end_time": 443676.0,
      "text": "or engage with them in conversation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 443700.0,
      "end_time": 446556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard. It&#39;s not easy, and I&#39;m making this very personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 446580.0,
      "end_time": 447955.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s actually more traumatic"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 447980.0,
      "end_time": 450716.0,
      "text": "than some of the big issues that I work on in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 450740.0,
      "end_time": 452580.0,
      "text": "entertaining my kids at dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 453380.0,
      "end_time": 456516.0,
      "text": "But what it does is it connects them here in the present with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 456540.0,
      "end_time": 457796.0,
      "text": "but it also --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 457820.0,
      "end_time": 461276.0,
      "text": "and this is the crux of transgenerational thinking ethics --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 461300.0,
      "end_time": 464596.0,
      "text": "it sets them up to how they&#39;re going to interact with their kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 464620.0,
      "end_time": 466700.0,
      "text": "and their kids and their kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 468180.0,
      "end_time": 469860.0,
      "text": "Second, futures thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 470500.0,
      "end_time": 472476.0,
      "text": "When we think about the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 472500.0,
      "end_time": 473740.0,
      "text": "10, 15 years out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 474740.0,
      "end_time": 476598.0,
      "text": "give me a vision of what the future is."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 477820.0,
      "end_time": 480476.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t have to give it to me, but think in your head."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 480500.0,
      "end_time": 482636.0,
      "text": "And what you&#39;re probably going to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 482660.0,
      "end_time": 484476.0,
      "text": "is the dominant cultural lens"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 484500.0,
      "end_time": 487556.0,
      "text": "that dominates our thinking about the future right now:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 487580.0,
      "end_time": 488780.0,
      "text": "technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 489660.0,
      "end_time": 491396.0,
      "text": "So when we think about the problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 491420.0,
      "end_time": 493596.0,
      "text": "we always put it through a technological lens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 493620.0,
      "end_time": 496876.0,
      "text": "a tech-centric, a techno-utopia, and there&#39;s nothing wrong with that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 496900.0,
      "end_time": 500195.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s something that we have to really think deeply about"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 500220.0,
      "end_time": 503760.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;re going to move on these major issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 503100.0,
      "end_time": 505156.0,
      "text": "because it wasn&#39;t always like this. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 505180.0,
      "end_time": 507820.0,
      "text": "The ancients had their way of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 508660.0,
      "end_time": 510180.0,
      "text": "about what the future was."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 511460.0,
      "end_time": 516356.0,
      "text": "The Church definitely had their idea of what the future could be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 516380.0,
      "end_time": 519316.0,
      "text": "and you could actually pay your way into that future. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 519340.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521276.00000000006,
      "text": "And luckily for humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 521299.0,
      "end_time": 523435.0,
      "text": "we got the scientific revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 523460.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525116.0,
      "text": "From there, we got the technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 525140.0,
      "end_time": 526795.0,
      "text": "but what has happened --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 526820.0,
      "end_time": 529180.0,
      "text": "And by the way, this is not a critique."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 530140.0,
      "end_time": 532516.0,
      "text": "I love technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 532540.0,
      "end_time": 534474.0,
      "text": "Everything in my house talks back to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 534499.0,
      "end_time": 536676.0,
      "text": "from my children to my speakers to everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 536700.0,
      "end_time": 539516.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 539540.0,
      "end_time": 545236.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ve abdicated the future from the high priests in Rome"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 548340.0,
      "text": "to the high priests of Silicon Valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 549700.0,
      "end_time": 553360.0,
      "text": "So when we think, well, how are we going to deal with climate"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 553600.0,
      "end_time": 554636.0,
      "text": "or with poverty or homelessness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 554660.0,
      "end_time": 557780.0,
      "text": "our first reaction is to think about it through a technology lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 558900.0,
      "end_time": 563516.0,
      "text": "And look, I&#39;m not advocating that we go to this guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 563540.0,
      "end_time": 565459.0,
      "text": "I love Joel, don&#39;t get me wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 566220.0,
      "end_time": 567876.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m not saying we go to Joel."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 567900.0,
      "end_time": 569716.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m saying is we have to rethink"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 569740.0,
      "end_time": 574516.0,
      "text": "our base assumption about only looking at the future in one way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 574540.0,
      "end_time": 576675.0,
      "text": "only looking at it through the dominant lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 576700.0,
      "end_time": 578876.0,
      "text": "Because our problems are so big and so vast"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 578900.0,
      "end_time": 581716.0,
      "text": "that we need to open ourselves up."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 581740.0,
      "end_time": 585460.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s why I do everything in my power not to talk about the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 586140.0,
      "end_time": 587860.0,
      "text": "I talk about futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 588740.0,
      "end_time": 590476.0,
      "text": "It opens the conversation again."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 590500.0,
      "end_time": 592956.0,
      "text": "So when you&#39;re sitting and thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 592980.0,
      "end_time": 596156.0,
      "text": "about how do we move forward on this major issue --"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 596180.0,
      "end_time": 597715.0,
      "text": "it could be at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 597740.0,
      "end_time": 599716.0,
      "text": "it could be at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 599740.0,
      "end_time": 602596.0,
      "text": "it could be again on the global stage --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 602620.0,
      "end_time": 607360.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t cut yourself off from thinking about something beyond technology as a fix"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 607600.0,
      "end_time": 610595.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re more concerned about technological evolution right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 610620.0,
      "end_time": 612756.0,
      "text": "than we are about moral evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 612780.0,
      "end_time": 614795.0,
      "text": "And unless we fix for that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 614820.0,
      "end_time": 617396.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not going to be able to get out of short-termism"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 617420.0,
      "end_time": 619236.0,
      "text": "and get to where we want to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 622200.0,
      "text": "The final, telos thinking. This comes from the Greek root."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 622500.0,
      "end_time": 624756.0,
      "text": "Ultimate aim and ultimate purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 624780.0,
      "end_time": 627140.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s really asking one question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 627940.0,
      "end_time": 629140.0,
      "text": "to what end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 630100.0,
      "end_time": 633116.0,
      "text": "When was the last time you asked yourself: To what end?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 633140.0,
      "end_time": 636939.0,
      "text": "And when you asked yourself that, how far out did you go?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 637460.0,
      "end_time": 640460.0,
      "text": "Because long isn&#39;t long enough anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 641380.0,
      "end_time": 643276.0,
      "text": "Three, five years doesn&#39;t cut it."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 643300.0,
      "end_time": 645579.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 30, 40, 50, 100 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 646620.0,
      "end_time": 648836.0,
      "text": "In Homer&#39;s epic, \"The Odyssey,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 648860.0,
      "end_time": 651916.0,
      "text": "Odysseus had the answer to his \"what end.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 651940.0,
      "end_time": 653340.0,
      "text": "It was Ithaca."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 653700.0,
      "end_time": 655796.0,
      "text": "It was this bold vision of what he wanted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 655820.0,
      "end_time": 657196.0,
      "text": "to return to Penelope."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 657220.0,
      "end_time": 659836.0,
      "text": "And I can tell you, because of the work that I&#39;m doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 659860.0,
      "end_time": 662716.0,
      "text": "but also you know it intuitively -- we have lost our Ithaca."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 662740.0,
      "end_time": 666276.0,
      "text": "We have lost our \"to what end,\" so we stay on this hamster wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 666300.0,
      "end_time": 668476.0,
      "text": "And yes, we&#39;re trying to solve these problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 668500.0,
      "end_time": 671340.0,
      "text": "but what comes after we solve the problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 671980.0,
      "end_time": 675220.0,
      "text": "And unless you define what comes after, people aren&#39;t going to move."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 676220.0,
      "end_time": 678636.0,
      "text": "The businesses -- this isn&#39;t just about business --"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 678660.0,
      "end_time": 681996.0,
      "text": "but the businesses that do consistently, who break out of short-termism"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 682200.0,
      "end_time": 684360.0,
      "text": "not surprisingly are family-run businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 684600.0,
      "end_time": 687636.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re transgenerational. They&#39;re telos. They think about the futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 687660.0,
      "end_time": 691356.0,
      "text": "And this is an ad for Patek Philippe. They&#39;re 175 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 691380.0,
      "end_time": 694436.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s amazing is that they literally embody"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 694460.0,
      "end_time": 697276.0,
      "text": "this kind of longpathian sense in their brand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 697300.0,
      "end_time": 700195.0,
      "text": "because, by the way, you never actually own a Patek Philippe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 700220.0,
      "end_time": 701796.0,
      "text": "and I definitely won&#39;t --"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 701820.0,
      "end_time": 702836.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 702860.0,
      "end_time": 705860.0,
      "text": "unless somebody wants to just throw 25,000 dollars on the stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 705884.0,
      "end_time": 709840.0,
      "text": "You merely look after it for the next generation."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 710660.0,
      "end_time": 713116.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s important that we remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 713140.0,
      "end_time": 716276.0,
      "text": "the future, we treat it like a noun."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 716300.0,
      "end_time": 718555.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not. It&#39;s a verb."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 718580.0,
      "end_time": 719836.0,
      "text": "It requires action."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 719860.0,
      "end_time": 721676.0,
      "text": "It requires us to push into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 721700.0,
      "end_time": 723636.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not this thing that washes over us."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 723660.0,
      "end_time": 726315.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that we actually have total control over."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 726340.0,
      "end_time": 729236.0,
      "text": "But in a short-term society, we end up feeling like we don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 729260.0,
      "end_time": 730596.0,
      "text": "We feel like we&#39;re trapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 730620.0,
      "end_time": 731820.0,
      "text": "We can push through that."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 733820.0,
      "end_time": 736260.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m getting more comfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 737200.0,
      "end_time": 739260.0,
      "text": "in the fact that at some point"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 740180.0,
      "end_time": 741459.0,
      "text": "in the inevitable future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 742820.0,
      "end_time": 744200.0,
      "text": "I will die."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 745600.0,
      "end_time": 749156.0,
      "text": "But because of these new ways of thinking and doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 749180.0,
      "end_time": 753116.0,
      "text": "both in the outside world and also with my family at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 753140.0,
      "end_time": 756276.0,
      "text": "and what I&#39;m leaving my kids, I get more comfortable in that fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 756300.0,
      "end_time": 759435.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s something that a lot of us are really uncomfortable with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 759460.0,
      "end_time": 760660.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m telling you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 761660.0,
      "end_time": 763760.0,
      "text": "think it through."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 763100.0,
      "end_time": 765836.0,
      "text": "Apply this type of thinking and you can push yourself past"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 765860.0,
      "end_time": 767916.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s inevitably very, very uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 767940.0,
      "end_time": 771660.0,
      "text": "And it all begins really with yourself asking this question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 772660.0,
      "end_time": 774420.0,
      "text": "What is your longpath?"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 775700.0,
      "end_time": 778596.0,
      "text": "But I ask you, when you ask yourself that"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 778620.0,
      "end_time": 780876.0,
      "text": "now or tonight or behind a steering wheel"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 780900.0,
      "end_time": 784260.0,
      "text": "or in the boardroom or the situation room:"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 786140.0,
      "end_time": 788316.0,
      "text": "push past the longpath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 788340.0,
      "end_time": 791636.0,
      "text": "quick, oh, what&#39;s my longpath the next three years or five years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 791660.0,
      "end_time": 795276.0,
      "text": "Try and push past your own life if you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 795300.0,
      "end_time": 797675.0,
      "text": "because it makes you do things a little bit bigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 797700.0,
      "end_time": 799380.0,
      "text": "than you thought were possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 800620.0,
      "end_time": 803620.0,
      "text": "Yes, we have huge, huge problems out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 805620.0,
      "end_time": 808200.0,
      "text": "With this process, with this thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 808940.0,
      "end_time": 810540.0,
      "text": "I think we can make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 811600.0,
      "end_time": 813595.0,
      "text": "I think you can make a difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 813620.0,
      "end_time": 815236.0,
      "text": "and I believe in you guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 815260.0,
      "end_time": 816476.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 816500.0,
      "end_time": 821523.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}